"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.14.1.8\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.14.1.8</span> 標題：在本章其他地方討論過的聖殿其他建築物和構件</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">梁木 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.5.3 大梁、樑木、椽子 (crossbeam, rafter)&lt;REALIA:3.1.5.3&gt;</a></h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>鏈子 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.21.4 鎖鏈、鏈子 (chain)&lt;REALIA:3.21.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>庭院 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.20 院子、院宇、宮廷 (courtyard, court)&lt;REALIA:3.20&gt;</a></p>\n<p>門 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2 門、門口 (door, doorway)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>門柱 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.4 門柱 (doorpost)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>堡壘 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.2 要塞、堡壘、城堡 (fortress, stronghold, castle, citadel, fort)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>地基 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.1 地基、根基、基礎 (foundation)&lt;REALIA:3.1.1&gt;</a></p>\n<p>大門／城門 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.5 城門 (city gate)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>門口 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.3 房屋或建築群的大門或大門入口 (gate or gateway to house or building complex)&lt;REALIA:3.1.3&gt;</a></p>\n<p>護衛室 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.5.2 護衛室、守衛房 (guardroom)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.5.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>合頁、鉸鏈 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.3 合頁 (hinge)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.3&gt;</a></p>\n<p>聖所 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.15.2.1 聖所、聖潔的地方 (Holy Place)&lt;REALIA:3.15.2.1&gt;</a></p>\n<p>門楣 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.5 門楣 (lintel)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>至聖所 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.15.2.2 至聖所、最聖潔的地方 (Holy of Holies, Most Holy Place)&lt;REALIA:3.15.2.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>柱頂上的網 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.5 柱子、柱頂 (column, pillar, capital)&lt;REALIA:3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>柱子 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.5 柱子、柱頂 (column, pillar, capital)&lt;REALIA:3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>屋頂 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.5 屋頂、房頂 (roof, housetop)&lt;REALIA:3.1.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>樓梯、臺階、階梯 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.7 樓梯、臺階、階梯 (stairs, steps)&lt;REALIA:3.1.7&gt;</a></p>\n<p>樓層 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.6.3 牆 (wall)&lt;REALIA:3.1.6.3&gt;</a> 和<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.6.4 樓上的房間、樓房、屋頂的房間 (upper room, roof chamber)&lt;REALIA:3.1.6.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>門檻 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.6 門檻 (threshold, doorsill)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.6&gt;</a></p>\n<p>窗戶 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.4 窗戶 (window)&lt;REALIA:3.1.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>牆 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.6 邊界牆、圍牆、圍欄、柵欄 (boundary wall, fence)&lt;REALIA:3.6&gt;</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>",
